# experimental: get battery levels via bluetooth
#
# -cups: dont need bluetooth printers, use wifi
# -mesh: dont enable mesh support (who uses this seriously?)
net-wireless/bluez experimental -cups -mesh

# note: pulls in pandoc/ghc/haskell stuff if man left in
#       if you already have installed safe to leave 'man' use flag on
media-sound/bluez-alsa man

